title: Bird Box, Roma, and Mental Health Access
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda talks with Humberto and Drane about the movies "Bird Box" and "Roma", and later Kirk interviews Dr. Paul Berry about Thero.org which is a free directory for mental health.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

Feb 16, 2019.

Email: Contact@PsychologyInSeattle.com

Access archive at: https://psychologyinseattle.squarespace.com

Become a patron of our podcast by going to https://www.patreon.com/PsychologyInSeattle

Music by Bread Knife Incident.
